	</head>
	<body>
	
			<section id="header">
				<header class="image centered">
					<img id="spons" src="static/spons_logo.png">
					<br>
					Presents
					<br>
					<br>
					<img id="logo" src="static/logo.png">
					<h1>Labyrinthos</h1>
					<p>An online treasure hunt</p>
				</header>
				<footer>
					<a href="#login" class="button style2 ">Login</a>
					<a href="#register" class="button style2 ">Register</a>
					<a href="#rules" class="button style2 ">Rules</a>
					<a href="/play" class="button style2 ">Play</a>
					<a href="/leaderboard" class="button style2 ">Leaderboard</a>
				</footer>
			</section>

			<article id="login" class="container box style3">
				<header>
					<h2>Login</h2>
				</header>
				<form method="post" action="/login">
					<div class="row 50%">
						<input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{csrfToken}}">
						<div class="6u 12u$(mobile)">
							<label>Username</label>
							<input type="text" name="username" placeholder="Moksha ID" required />
						</div>
						<div class="6u$ 12u$(mobile)">
							<label>Password</label>
							<input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required/>
						</div>
						<div class="12u$">
							<ul class="actions">
								<li><input type="submit" value="Login"/></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</form>
			</article>
			
			<article id="register" class="container box style3">
				<header>
					<h2>Register</h2>
				</header>
				<form method="post" action="/register">
					<div class="row 50%">
						<input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{csrfToken}}">
						<div class="6u 12u$(mobile)">
							<label>Moksha ID of Captain</label>
							<input type="text" name="username" placeholder="Captain Moksha ID" required/>
						</div>
						<div class="6u 12u$(mobile)">
							<label>Password</label>
							<input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required/>
						</div>
						<div class="12u$">
							<ul class="actions">
								<li><input type="submit" value="Register"></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</form>
			</article>
		
			<article id="rules" class="container box style3">
				<section>
					<header>
						<h2>Rules</h2>
					</header>
					<ol class="default">
						<li>All the participants need to register for Mokshaâ€˜17 at the Official <a href="http://www.mokshansit.com">Moksha website</a> and use the same details for the online round.</li>
						<li>Cross-campus teams are allowed. More than one team from one college are also allowed.</li>
						<li>Teams can consist of 3 maximum members.</li>
						<li>The event will be held in 2 rounds: <br><u>Online Round</u><br>Top 5 team after the scheduled online round time will qualify for the next round.<br><u>Offline Round</u><br>This round will be held in the college premises. Rules for this round will be briefed once all the teams reach.</li>
						<li>No participant can be a member of more than one team.</li>
						<li>Organisers have the right to disqualify any team if found breaking any rule.</li>
						<li>In case of any discrepancy, the decision of organisers will be final and binding.</li>
					</ol>
				</section>
			</article>

		<section id="footer">
			<ul>
				<li><a href="http://facebook.com/events/251708241956711" class=""><span class="label">Facebook</span></a></li>
			</ul>
			<img id="moksha" src="static/mok.png">
			<div class="copyright image centered">
				<ul class="menu">
					<li>&copy; Labyrinthos. All rights reserved.</li><li>Design: <a href="http://html5up.net">HTML5 UP</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		{% if afterSignup %}
		<div id="countCont">
			<span id="countText">
				Registered Succesfully
			</span>
		</div>
		{% endif %}
